			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="The Book of Restored Gods is a record belonging to the death god Jergal, containing the list of fallen and resurrected gods across the Forgotten Realms.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;CINEMATICS/MOCAP: The various methods of opening this book do not need to be shown on screen. There can be a close-up of the character focusing or a closeup on the book itself when it opens." />
